#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Je veux modifier la façon dont le jeu s'affiche. Est-ce possible ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "No. At this moment &kappname; features only one theme."
msgid "No. At this moment &kspaceduel; features only one theme."
msgstr "Non. &kappname; n'a pour le moment qu'un seul thème disponible."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "J'ai commis une erreur. Puis-je l'annuler ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "No. &kappname; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgid "No. &kspaceduel; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"Non, &kappname; n'implante pas actuellement de fonctionnalité "
"<quote>d'annulation</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Je ne comprend pas quoi faire ! Y a t-il une astuce ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "No. &kappname; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature. However, if "
#| "you carefully read through the <link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game "
#| "Rules, Strategies and Tips</link> section you shouldn't have this problem."
msgid ""
"No. &kspaceduel; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature. However, if "
"you carefully read through the <link linkend=\"rules_and_tips\">Game Rules, "
"Strategies and Tips</link> section you shouldn't have this problem."
msgstr ""
"Non. &kappname; n'inclut pas de fonctionnalité de <quote>conseil</quote>. "
"Cependant, si vous lisez attentivement la section <link linkend="
"\"rules_and_tips\">Règles du jeu, stratégies et astuces</link>, vous n'aurez "
"pas ce problème."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
